e\", \"from\": 473, \"to\": 478}, {\"ngram\": \"individual qualifier\", \"from\": 515, \"to\": 535}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Credit: Martha Terry.\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 558, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 545, \"end\": 551, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Jones\", \"score\": 0.9992079261869976, \"rank\": 0.0007815980827136208, \"text\": \"Martha\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Jones\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Martha_Jones\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Credit\", \"from\": 537, \"to\": 543}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I just keep it all exciting for everybody,\\\" joked Ben Maher, following his round in the Olympic showjumping individual qualifier.\", \"from\": 560, \"to\": 690, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 611, \"end\": 620, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Maher\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Ben Maher\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Maher\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ben_Maher\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"everybody\", \"from\": 593, \"to\": 602}, {\"ngram\": \"his round\", \"from\": 632, \"to\": 641}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic showjumping individual qualifier\", \"from\": 645, \"to\": 689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are in so that's all that matters I guess.\", \"from\": 691, \"to\": 737, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It can quickly go from close to pole position tomorrow to not being in [the final], but I do not know what happened.\", \"from\": 738, \"to\": 854, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"pole position\", \"from\": 770, \"to\": 783}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She felt amazing today.\", \"from\": 856, \"to\": 880, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She was very, very lively outside already this morning, and she's very sensitive now.\", \"from\": 881, \"to\": 966, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"I do not know why.\", \"from\": 967, \"to\": 985, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Today she was on it and playing a bit in the warm-up but when I got in the ring she honestly was jumping as good, if not better, than the other days and to the point where I thought I'd just keep on [going for a fast] time.\\\"\", \"from\": 986, \"to\": 1210, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a bit\", \"from\": 1018, \"to\": 1023}, {\"ngram\": \"the warm-up\", \"from\": 1027, \"to\": 1038}, {\"ngram\": \"the ring\", \"from\": 1057, \"to\": 1065}, {\"ngram\": \"the other days\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1134}, {\"ngram\": \"the point\", \"from\": 1142, \"to\": 1151}, {\"ngram\": \"a fast] time\", \"from\": 1196, \"to\": 1208}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ahead of his round Ben had made a \\\"plan B\\\" option, should anything have gone wrong.\", \"from\": 1214, \"to\": 1297, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his round\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1232}, {\"ngram\": \"Ben\", \"from\": 1233, \"to\": 1236}, {\"ngram\": \"a \\\"plan B\\\" option\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1263}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 1272, \"to\": 1280}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"My target was 75sec with a fence down.\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1338, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My target\", \"from\": 1300, \"to\": 1309}, {\"ngram\": \"a fence\", \"from\": 1325, \"to\": 1332}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I know that's a little bit of a back to front way of looking at it, but a worst case scenario plan B.\", \"from\": 1339, \"to\": 1440, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1365}, {\"ngram\": \"a back\", \"from\": 1369, \"to\": 1375}, {\"ngram\": \"front way\", \"from\": 1379, \"to\": 1388}, {\"ngram\": \"B.\", \"from\": 1438, \"to\": 1440}]}, {\"sentence\": \"And I guess there is a big shadow by the wall now, maybe I should have just gone in and taken her over [to look at it],\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1441, \"to\": 1570, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big shadow\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1474}, {\"ngram\": \"the wall\", \"from\": 1478, \"to\": 1486}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She took a little bit of a look; she just rolled around the corner and as she took off, it just took her by surprise.\", \"from\": 1572, \"to\": 1690, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a little bit\", \"from\": 1582, \"to\": 1594}, {\"ngram\": \"a look\", \"from\": 1598, \"to\": 1604}, {\"ngram\": \"the corner\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1639}, {\"ngram\": \"surprise\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1689}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Luckily I am a little older and experienced and we made a quick recovery to get home.\\\"\", \"from\": 1691, \"to\": 1777, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a quick recovery\", \"from\": 1747, \"to\": 1763}, {\"ngram\": \"home\", \"from\": 1771, \"to\": 1775}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Ben said the courses in the Paris Olympic showjumping have \\\"been incredible\\\", describing them as \\\"fair\\\" but \\\"delicate\\\".\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1898, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1807, \"end\": 1812, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999987771844, \"rank\": 1.2228723540213978e-09, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ben\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1782}, {\"ngram\": \"the courses\", \"from\": 1788, \"to\": 1799}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"They are big obviously, but we expect that at the Olympics - but they are very fair and I do not think taking too much out of the horses, and they are ultimately our priority here,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 1900, \"to\": 2091, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1947, \"to\": 1959}, {\"ngram\": \"the horses\", \"from\": 2027, \"to\": 2037}, {\"ngram\": \"our priority\", \"from\": 2063, \"to\": 2075}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Today is always a difficult day, I think they got a fair amount of clear rounds but it's very, very easy for the higher ranked riders to just slip on the wrong side of the cut-off mark here, but we are in the Olympics and I am happy I am in [the final].\\\"\", \"from\": 2093, \"to\": 2348, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Today\", \"from\": 2094, \"to\": 2099}, {\"ngram\": \"a difficult day\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"a fair amount\", \"from\": 2144, \"to\": 2157}, {\"ngram\": \"clear rounds\", \"from\": 2161, \"to\": 2173}, {\"ngram\": \"the higher ranked riders\", \"from\": 2203, \"to\": 2227}, {\"ngram\": \"the wrong side\", \"from\": 2244, \"to\": 2258}, {\"ngram\": \"the cut-off mark\", \"from\": 2262, \"to\": 2278}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 2299, \"to\": 2311}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Tomorrow the scores go back to zero, meaning it's all to play for.\", \"from\": 2350, \"to\": 2416, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the scores\", \"from\": 2359, \"to\": 2369}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"That I am happy with right now,\\\" said Ben.\", \"from\": 2418, \"to\": 2461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Ben\", \"from\": 2457, \"to\": 2460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I could have been second last to go, and now I am going to be probably three or four in.\", \"from\": 2462, \"to\": 2551, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Dallas she's a very sensitive horse - but she's a great horse.\", \"from\": 2552, \"to\": 2614, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a very sensitive horse\", \"from\": 2565, \"to\": 2587}, {\"ngram\": \"a great horse\", \"from\": 2600, \"to\": 2613}]}, {\"sentence\": \"We are earlier in the morning tomorrow and I ride my own plan anyway, so sometimes you are better to go out from the beginning, do your thing, and let the others come behind.\", \"from\": 2615, \"to\": 2789, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the morning\", \"from\": 2633, \"to\": 2644}, {\"ngram\": \"my own plan\", \"from\": 2665, \"to\": 2676}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 2728, \"to\": 2741}, {\"ngram\": \"your thing\", \"from\": 2746, \"to\": 2756}, {\"ngram\": \"the others\", \"from\": 2766, \"to\": 2776}]}, {\"sentence\": \"So I hope we have had our mistake this week today.\\\"\", \"from\": 2790, \"to\": 2841, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"our mistake\", \"from\": 2812, \"to\": 2823}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Seventy-three combinations tackled the Olympic showjumping individual qualifier today, with 30 going through to tomorrow's (6 August) final.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2983, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Seventy-three combinations\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2869}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic showjumping individual qualifier\", \"from\": 2878, \"to\": 2922}, {\"ngram\": \"tomorrow's (6 August) final\", \"from\": 2955, \"to\": 2982}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All three Brits will compete for an individual medal, with bothHarry Charlesand Romeo 88 andScott Brashand Jefferson, both posting clear rounds today.\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3135, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"All three Brits\", \"from\": 2985, \"to\": 3000}, {\"ngram\": \"an individual medal\", \"from\": 3018, \"to\": 3037}, {\"ngram\": \"bothHarry\", \"from\": 3044, \"to\": 3053}, {\"ngram\": \"Charlesand Romeo\", \"from\": 3054, \"to\": 3070}, {\"ngram\": \"clear rounds\", \"from\": 3116, \"to\": 3128}]}, {\"sentence\": \"They will be joined by showjumping heavyweights including Frenchman Julien Epaillard and Dubai Du Cedre - who top the standings and will jump last tomorrow -Henrik von Eckermannand King Edward, Ireland's Shane Sweetnam and James Kann Cruz and Daniel Coyle with Legacy, European championsSteve Guerdatand Dynamix De Belheme, andMartin Fuchsand Leone Jei for Switzerland.\", \"from\": 3136, \"to\": 3505, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3225,